item.title: CVE-2017-7507|2024-08-05T16:04:11.924Z -- gnutls -- gnutls
item.description: GnuTLS version 3.5.12 and earlier is vulnerable to a NULL pointer dereference while decoding a status response TLS extension with valid contents. This could lead to a crash of the GnuTLS server application.
